text: Lisianski (Lisiansky, Lisyansky) may refer to one of the following. *Yuri Feodorovich Lisyansky, an officer in the Imperial Russian Navy and explorer *Things named after Lisyansky: **Lisianski Island, Hawaii **Lisianski Peninsula, located on the west coast of Baranof Island in the Alaska Panhandle. **Lisianski Mountain, Sakhalin **Lisianski Strait, at the northern end of Chichagof Island, Alaska **Lisianski Bay **Cape Lisianski
title: Lisianski
